Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Club AT-X采访映像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「玛利亚狂热」剧中扮演宫前加奈子的真田麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「玛利亚狂热」剧中扮演祇堂鞠也的小林优
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是「玛利亚狂热」剧中扮演茉莉花的井上麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「玛利亚狂热」第一话决定在AT-X先行放送了  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作为第一话的前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天将就本片向大家进行简单介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆直接剧透好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧透！剧透！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气透干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天为了能让大家更加深入了解本片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横入？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  横入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们三个来介绍片中看点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}「玛利亚狂热」讲的是一个什么样的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.26,0:01:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  感想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这哪算简介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超绝  超刺激  爱情喜剧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把重要的东西漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合趣味少女和…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超S  超S少年的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女装超S少年的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超绝？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没萝卜的事  绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超合金？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超合金？有超合金萝卜出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是萝卜片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有会出来的感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有那么一点那样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实萝卜是不会出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演的宫前加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个超喜欢女孩子的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓百合趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事由她转入天之妃女子学园后正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很有贵族女校风的学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很高雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里呢  我所扮演的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少女  一眼看去是美少女  实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小子  你搞什么飞机」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的一个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许正是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉优凭空就能演绎出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望优去演真人版  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  麦克风…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别的…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻里奈的话我听着好高兴  有种不得不加油的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来演真人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面请扮演我的女仆的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是演佣人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱的茉莉花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说我在剧中总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是情绪低落的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血压也比较低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么特别的感情起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  又特别的毒舌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒舌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上经常是「母猪」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常被这样骂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你这家伙」之类的不满的话也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多话让人觉得「这种话能说吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待本篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}饰演角色的感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子应该说是个节奏很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说情绪变换很激烈的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉呢  真的扮演起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现与其说是女高中生  分明就是个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思维回路似乎是男性的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像男孩子的那种「这女孩真可爱  哈哈」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但加奈子的这种言行  又让大家觉得很亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边喊着「真可爱」一边一次一次地吐…喷鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是逆流了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里出来就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有很多东西流出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多东西流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之饰演女孩子的感觉在渐渐变淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  饰演前后的感觉最不一样的就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉加奈子的台词量不是一般的多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉八成以上都是加奈子的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们十分的过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过更辛苦的要说是鞠也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉经常转换角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来回来去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全相反的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子和女孩子的两种角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得是个十分可爱  待人热情的圣母型角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「搞什么飞机啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咚」地一声就变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再学了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才给大家学过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「咣」地变过来  再变回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  一个经常像这样得到大家帮助的祇堂鞠也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个超有加奈子的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说呢  虽说是男性  却扮成女性来欺骗大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标好多  这样一比划的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人员的人数都泄露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是一个有很多工作人员的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快乐又好玩的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你一个没什么起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就我一个很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想进入这种氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「过来吧你」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到脚了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉  因为这是早上的录制现场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上配音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能以早上那种低落的情绪进入现场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会那么干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这反而是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  毕竟是早上的现场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  没错  就是早上拼命提高情绪后才进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我一两句的台词特别多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说的正热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我在旁边冒出一句「母猪」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是跟不上节奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己总觉得不该打乱这个气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说台词的时候总是七上八下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样站在麦克风前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一边想着  可不能拖大家后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七上八下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了！  像这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的一个现场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种现场  真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}还有什么其他角色登场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如同班的幸啊  弓弦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有奈奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐里的隆显姐姐  绚璃学姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿管老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿管老师  与那国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍地都是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这学校里只有美少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  让我十分满足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词里也有一句
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子说过2-B的谁谁谁很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2-B的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田和…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁谁  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之大家都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  就像在楼梯间碰到的谁谁也很可爱…的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在说的这人得多迷女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且宿舍也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是女生宿舍  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一天24小时都很满足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的监视之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  两人是一个房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩是一个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是让她吃了很大的苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是监视与被监视的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被男孩子摸到后会起荨麻疹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都是被鞠也诱惑  然后被摸  「荨麻疹啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要～荨麻疹啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉话越说越乱了  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家被吸引后一定会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「她们在说什么啊  是什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就明白了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢  让人忍不住想去见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}录音现场的气氛如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场的气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我可以说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事  说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样  大家并排坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录音的时候我坐在正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边就是她们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们夹着她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们夹着她坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这个不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有时会变  但基本是这样三个人坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后旁边会坐着其他的声优
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都坐得很近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为录音的都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像在班里大家叽叽喳喳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是女子学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很华丽的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是只有你们三位在炒气氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天绝对是…说出「今天」了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一言我一语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就是气氛特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先表现一下气氛有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过节一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁那么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确实是个欢乐的现场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉总是在笑呢  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得肯定能看到有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就这样起哄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像真田总是想着「会不会有啥捏他出现呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为演的是加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉在录音现场我的地位和剧中角色差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在给你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美姐加油  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  我们都在给你打气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}OPED的曲目是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HANAJI
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HANAJI
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  鼻血嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你这么来一次呢  比如在搞活动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观众们也一起来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里到这里来这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是优喷得最壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  又踩到脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加入表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈要求把这动作加进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞美老师也希望大家也来一起这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必大家看到歌名可能会想这是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是如大家想的那样  鼻血而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语里的这个单词还有别的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一开始看到革命歌名的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会有人怀疑看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感觉就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HA  NA…JI？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怀疑是不是BI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火？…啊不对  JI？这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血一般不会被当作歌名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HA  NA  JI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI的时候这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JI的时候这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一首超级激烈的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首很可爱的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:14:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要只注意这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子也很欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲风是很欢乐的  请一定要在活动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能搞热气氛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家一起来做这个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样大家能开心的话  我们也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一首鲜明表现「玛丽亚狂热」世界的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让这首曲子能为全剧添彩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微活跃一下气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是ED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由我们三个演唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱团  不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱队？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天之妃少女合唱团」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…团」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:15:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取了这么棒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是电子乐味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是翻唱Yellow Magic Orchestra的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫「给你，心跳。」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的角色会展示个性的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到点传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像茉莉花唱这首歌时发生了点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你搞得那么故弄玄虚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉实在想象不到茉莉花会怎么唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  就拼命想怎样才像茉莉花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始打算唱得可爱些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可马上就想  不对  这不是茉莉花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始的时候完全是被你们俩带着走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来实在是不唱不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情的话开始时还有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来因为曲子太长  渐渐有点烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲也越来越小  这样就稍微有点茉莉花的感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后就是边唱边叹气的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还没完啊」那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来因为录了两遍  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分被编辑成了啥样我就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家唱的时候确实都是很有个性的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望能让那部分保留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}对观众们的寄语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  「玛利亚狂热」即将开始播放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说片子里充满了让人眼花缭乱的剧情展开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家观看时一定要紧盯着荧幕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连细微的地方也不要放过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有各位角色都很有个性  很有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请找出自己喜欢的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起满足吧  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位  「玛利亚狂热」可谓独一无二  前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是超绝  超棒的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很超绝  超刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家一定  一定不要被甩下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才得到工作人员同意了  这点程度的动作没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克掉了可不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不要被甩下  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家扮演的角色也都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很帅  很有个性的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像鞠也就是  既有可爱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有「你这百合女」这样的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的角色也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和大家一起品味「玛利亚狂热」的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后注意不要被甩掉  尽情享受片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请大家关注本片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交接
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是扮演茉莉花的井上麻里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这是部刺激又快节奏的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一不留神就会错过很多情节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请大家一定要睁大眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外离画面一米以上观看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部片子里真是充满了个性十足的女孩男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会有许多各式各样性格的角色登场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请一定要怀着加奈子的那种情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊  这孩子真可爱」这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然大家是不会喷鼻血的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也要像喷鼻血般气势十足地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边这样  一边观看本片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「玛利亚狂热」今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧





